## Overview

uptime Kuma is an open source and self-hosted monitoring tool that is responsible for uptime tracking of services, network devices, and websites. 
supporting multiple monitor types (HTTP/HTTPS, TCP, DNS, ping, etc.), uptime KUMA is a logical and effective application for any home network.

